Mei, good work today.
Were you nervous? Did everything go okay?

Nah~ I was seriously trembling! It was intense!
But hey! More importantly──
──It was fun!

Asahi-chan was so energetic!
She was super cool with her moves!

Fuyuko-chan was so cute!
She was totally fluttering~!

Haha, I see. But Mei,
you were shining too, not losing to them.

Really? I was so desperate
that I didn't feel it at all~ Ahaha...
Is the unit going well?
Of course!

Asahi-chan sometimes runs ahead in a surprising way,
I really respect that since I can't think of doing it.

Fuyuko-chan is probably a worrier,
she often holds her head.

But she's a caring person, so she keeps an eye on Asahi-chan,
she's a really strong support! They're both amazing!

I see... yeah, that's right.
I'm glad Mei said that.

H-Hey, what's up? Producer-san,
you're smiling strangely.

Oh, sorry. It's nothing.
...Do you think we'll get along?

Huh? What's with that question?
Getting along isn't about whether you can or can't.
That kind of thing just happens naturally, right?
